01:18:49.960 --> 01:18:52.679
And I've lost my house...

01:18:52.680 --> 01:18:54.280
all the money.

01:18:55.800 --> 01:18:59.480
Fucking Inland Revenue are after me.
You know?

01:19:03.560 --> 01:19:06.319
I'll even give up the drink, Barry.

01:19:06.320 --> 01:19:07.919
I promise.

01:19:07.920 --> 01:19:11.480
You wouldn't last a day, Alex. I-I'm sorry.

01:19:13.960 --> 01:19:16.199
We can do this.

01:19:16.200 --> 01:19:20.359
You know? I could change and...

01:19:20.360 --> 01:19:22.840
You're the only one who can help me.

01:19:26.800 --> 01:19:28.800
I've lost my family.

01:19:32.480 --> 01:19:35.159
Alex, you're a mess.

01:19:35.160 --> 01:19:36.560
Look, um...

01:19:37.920 --> 01:19:41.759
Look, where you headed to? I'll get
Robbo to give you a lift somewhere.

01:19:41.760 --> 01:19:43.600
I've nowhere to go.

01:19:45.440 --> 01:19:46.880
It's...

01:19:48.720 --> 01:19:51.400
I'm sure you know a boozer
open somewhere near here.

01:19:53.400 --> 01:19:54.880
Take it, Alex.

01:20:04.040 --> 01:20:05.680
Take care, Alex.

01:20:12.000 --> 01:20:14.759
COMMENTATOR: Alex Higgins concedes.

01:20:14.760 --> 01:20:18.959
Steve James has played exceptionally well.

01:20:18.960 --> 01:20:22.679
From 5-5 he won five frames in succession

01:20:22.680 --> 01:20:24.920
to win by 10 frames to 5.

01:20:27.880 --> 01:20:30.399
I actually owe Higgins my life.

01:20:30.400 --> 01:20:34.439
True story, right? I was getting
beaten up by three blokes

01:20:34.440 --> 01:20:37.039
and Alex walks round the corner and says,

01:20:37.040 --> 01:20:38.639
"That's probably enough now, lads."

01:20:38.640 --> 01:20:41.920
THEY LAUGH

01:21:00.760 --> 01:21:02.679
Alex.

01:21:02.680 --> 01:21:04.959
Hey, Alex.

01:21:04.960 --> 01:21:08.399
- Why are you even over? I ain't coming to your...
- Just saying, mate.

01:21:08.400 --> 01:21:10.720
- Get the fuck off.
- OK, man.

01:21:14.160 --> 01:21:15.960
Give me another drink, someone.

01:21:49.480 --> 01:21:51.280
How many's he had now?

01:21:53.240 --> 01:21:54.839
Maybe I should go down.

01:21:54.840 --> 01:21:57.519
No, Jimmy. Leave him.

01:21:57.520 --> 01:21:59.400
He won't thank you.

01:22:22.840 --> 01:22:24.360
One more.

01:22:46.800 --> 01:22:48.040
Alex.

01:22:50.800 --> 01:22:52.160
(Fuck off.)

01:22:53.640 --> 01:22:55.480
What are you doing down here?

01:22:56.840 --> 01:22:59.759
- Come to get you, Alex, come on.
- Fuck off.

01:22:59.760 --> 01:23:03.560
- They're turning the lights off, Alex.
- Don't need you to help me.

01:23:04.720 --> 01:23:06.440
I don't need anyone.

01:23:10.520 --> 01:23:14.360
I...fucking... quit.

01:23:18.720 --> 01:23:20.839
You can relax, we'll call it a draw.

01:23:20.840 --> 01:23:24.279
- I'm very sorry to hear that, Alex.
- No, you're not.

01:23:24.280 --> 01:23:26.639
You've got what you always wanted.

01:23:26.640 --> 01:23:29.679
You got rid of the Hurricane.

01:23:29.680 --> 01:23:33.119
You'll find out what it's like soon enough.

01:23:33.120 --> 01:23:36.879
Stephen Hendry will come along
and knock you off your perch

01:23:36.880 --> 01:23:38.920
and then you'll know what it's like.

01:23:40.880 --> 01:23:42.640
Why do you hate me?

01:23:44.080 --> 01:23:47.120
Come on, I don't hate you.
I've never hated you.

01:23:48.480 --> 01:23:49.920
I idolised you.

01:23:51.680 --> 01:23:54.839
When I watched you play I
thought it was genius.

01:23:54.840 --> 01:23:58.640
I wanted to be just like
Alex Higgins. Once.

01:24:01.560 --> 01:24:04.719
That's... That's... No.

01:24:04.720 --> 01:24:07.839
No, that's not true. We've...

01:24:07.840 --> 01:24:10.600
We've always been... enemies.

01:24:12.160 --> 01:24:13.879
I'm not your enemy, Alex.

01:24:13.880 --> 01:24:15.959
You are. And the drink.

01:24:15.960 --> 01:24:19.080
That's right, blame me. Everyone else does.

01:24:21.440 --> 01:24:23.120
You look after yourself.

01:24:24.560 --> 01:24:26.759
Remember this -

01:24:26.760 --> 01:24:30.559
I'll get the romantic
obituaries when I die.

01:24:30.560 --> 01:24:32.920
